    "Other technical limitations exist, in particular the use of different staining, microscopes, and assays for DNA fragmentation that can challenge the training of an accurate AI model.",
    "Guidelines for testing, and optimal techniques for testing sperm DNA fragmentation have been proposed 66, 67, but testing is still not widely recommended.",
    "Progress in this field thus relies on the standardization and optimization of DNA fragmentation assays, prospective evaluation of its impact on ART outcomes, and the development of therapies to improve sperm DNA fragmentation levels 68.",
